---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="py-20 bg-deep-navy border-t border-white/5 relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between gap-16 md:gap-8 mb-20 md:mb-32 relative z-10 mt-10">
    <!-- Brand Info (Left) -->
    <div class="md:w-1/2 flex flex-col justify-center">
      <div class="mb-10">
        <img id="footer-logo" src="/Scalo-logoWhite.png" alt="Scalo" class="h-16 md:h-20 w-auto" />
      </div>
      <p class="text-white text-base md:text-[17px] leading-relaxed font-outfit font-light max-w-md">
        Transformando datos complejos en decisiones estratégicas efectivas. Nuestra misión es empoderar a la próxima generación de startups.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Links & Socials (Right) -->
    <div class="md:w-1/2 flex flex-col md:items-end justify-center">
      <div class="w-full max-w-sm flex flex-col gap-14">
        <!-- Grid Links -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-x-8 gap-y-5 text-white font-outfit font-normal text-[15px]">
          <a href="/#features" class="hover:text-scalo-accent-cyan transition-colors">Funcionalidades</a>
          <a href="/#problema" class="hover:text-scalo-accent-cyan transition-colors">El problema</a>
          <a href="/#soluciones" class="hover:text-scalo-accent-cyan transition-colors">Soluciones</a>
          <a href="/blog" class="hover:text-scalo-accent-cyan transition-colors">Insights</a>
          <a href="/waitlist" class="hover:text-scalo-accent-cyan transition-colors">Private testing</a>
          <a href="mailto:hola@iterocompany.com" class="hover:text-scalo-accent-cyan transition-colors">Contacto</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Socials -->
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-[22px] text-white font-outfit font-bold mb-5 tracking-tight">Síganos en redes sociales</h4>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-6 text-white font-outfit font-normal text-[15px]">
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/scalolatam/" class="hover:text-scalo-accent-cyan transition-colors">LinkedIn</a>
            <a href="https://www.instagram.com/scalolatam/" class="hover:text-scalo-accent-cyan transition-colors">Instagram</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10 text-center font-outfit font-light text-slate-300 text-[15px]">
    <p>
      Un producto de <a href="https://iterocompany.com/" rel="Itero Company" class="text-white hover:text-scalo-accent-cyan transition-colors font-normal">Itero Company</a> • Hecho con ❤️ por scalo team
    </p>
  </div>
  
  <!-- Subtle Gradient Decoration -->
  <div class="absolute -bottom-24 -left-24 w-72 h-72 bg-scalo-primary/10 blur-[120px] rounded-full"></div>
  <div class="absolute -bottom-24 -right-24 w-72 h-72 bg-scalo-accent-violet/10 blur-[120px] rounded-full"></div>
</footer>
